  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your problem-solving skills to the test in <strong>Wet</strong>, a puzzle game where manipulating terrain and guiding water is the key to relaxing challenges and tricky trials. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/1c34b88f8eb1880528ebf4a85a65fb90.poster.avif?t=1746524118\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/1c34b88f8eb1880528ebf4a85a65fb90.webm?t=1746524118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/1c34b88f8eb1880528ebf4a85a65fb90.mp4?t=1746524118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raise and lower the land to create pathways and control where the water flows. Each puzzle presents unique challenges, forcing you to think creatively and strategically in the beautiful, calming landscape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for puzzle lovers with a creative streak, who enjoy a mix of tactile feedback and brain-teasing gameplay. Wet offers a relaxing yet stimulating cozy puzzle experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/3daec025213e2b7142b453d571e279d4.poster.avif?t=1746524118\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/3daec025213e2b7142b453d571e279d4.webm?t=1746524118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/3daec025213e2b7142b453d571e279d4.mp4?t=1746524118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >32 dynamic puzzles to challenge your mind </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique terrain manipulation mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Water flow simulation for complex problem-solving</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful, calming landscapes with soothing sounds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless replayability - try to complete each puzzle in the fewest possible terrain moves</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against others via Leaderboards</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get your problem-solving skills flowing, one puzzle at a time! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/0cc7972dcd1d9b72e5044d8230669c3d.poster.avif?t=1746524118\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/0cc7972dcd1d9b72e5044d8230669c3d.webm?t=1746524118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/0cc7972dcd1d9b72e5044d8230669c3d.mp4?t=1746524118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your problem-solving skills to the test in <strong>Wet</strong>, a puzzle game where manipulating terrain and guiding water is the key to relaxing challenges and tricky trials. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/1c34b88f8eb1880528ebf4a85a65fb90.poster.avif?t=1746524118\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/1c34b88f8eb1880528ebf4a85a65fb90.webm?t=1746524118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/1c34b88f8eb1880528ebf4a85a65fb90.mp4?t=1746524118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raise and lower the land to create pathways and control where the water flows. Each puzzle presents unique challenges, forcing you to think creatively and strategically in the beautiful, calming landscape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for puzzle lovers with a creative streak, who enjoy a mix of tactile feedback and brain-teasing gameplay. Wet offers a relaxing yet stimulating cozy puzzle experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/3daec025213e2b7142b453d571e279d4.poster.avif?t=1746524118\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/3daec025213e2b7142b453d571e279d4.webm?t=1746524118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447390/extras/3daec025213e2b7142b453d571e279d4.mp4?t=1746524118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></s